Create a list of analysis from a results table

create_loa_from_results.Rd

Create a list of analysis from a results table

Usage

create_loa_from_results(results_table, analysis_key_column = "analysis_key")

Arguments

results_table

Results table with an analysis key

analysis_key_column

character vector with the name of the analysis key column. Default is "analysis key"

Value

a list of analysis

Examples

create_loa_from_results(analysistools_MSNA_template_with_ratio_results_table$results_table)
